%F A061347 Dirichlet g.f.: zeta(s)*(1-1/3^(s-1)). - _R. J. Mathar_, Feb 09 2011
%F A061347 a(n) = n * Sum_{k=1..n} binomial(k,n-k)/k*(-1)^(k+1). - _Dmitry Kruchinin_, Jun 03 2011
